[normal]Geoffrey and Julia Queen – Written evidence[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]As residents of The Yorkshire Dales National Park we are strongly opposed to the desecration of historic Green Lanes in the area by recreational  4 x 4 vehicles and motor  cycles.  These are causing irreparable damage to the environment, noise pollution and detrimental effect to wildlife.
[normal]&#xa0;
