[normal]We also expressly support the formal submissions made by The Green Lanes Environmental Action Group (GLEAG), by The Green Lanes Protection Group (GLPG), by The Peak District Green Lanes Alliance (PDGLA) and our own Yorkshire Dales Green Lanes Alliance (YDGLA).
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]We trust these proposals will be considered.
